item.title: I cant get onto anyones server please help! :(
item.dc:creator: @god_of_ikiliki god of ikiliki
item.description:
@god_of_ikiliki wrote:

I mean…,

To run a server you have a source,
Their 2 files called compile.bat and runserver.bat
The server owner need to run the runserver.bat and mopar and a other program to make server names,

The server is down if he isnt running runserver.bat and the program and mopar or a other client.
So the problem is becouse u cant get in the server isnt on (isnt running compile.bat etc.)

To see what servers are on go to:

http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php

or

http://www.dodian.com/index.php?page=status

or

www.rs-server.net (need registration, but has the most servers in the status page)
